  "note": [
    "Where every REAL E2/E3 stimulus comes from. This file is the intent (which",
    "person, brand, or place each item denotes); stimuli.lock.json is the record",
    "of what was actually resolved and downloaded, and is what makes a later",
    "fetch reproducible. Edit this file, then re-run the fetcher with --relock.",
    "",
    "Only freely-licensed Wikimedia Commons files are permitted. The fetcher",
    "refuses anything outside its licence allow-list rather than downloading it,",
    "because a non-free logo is exactly what this repo must not redistribute."
  ],
