    "E3": {
      "note": [
        "E3 probes exposure to a TOPIC, so a card only carries the recognition",
        "effect if the participant plausibly HANDLED that kind of document. These",
        "eight are documents most people have actually held: a vaccination card,",
        "a nutrition label, a public-health poster, a census form, an 'I Voted'",
        "sticker, a recycling poster, a jury summons, a payslip. It is 3 health /",
        "3 civic / 1 legal / 1 finance because Wikimedia Commons has canonical",
        "free versions for health and civic but not for the modern US finance and",
        "legal forms (a current 1040, W-2, Miranda card) -- those are public",
        "domain but simply not on Commons. Finance and legal are therefore present",
        "but too thin to carry a per-category claim. See public/stimuli/README.md."
      ],
